
= African [[Coworking]] labs

URL = http://jokkolabs.net/en/

=Description=

"Mixing the spirits of “techlabs”, « innovation hub », coworking space, incubators and « think tank »…JOKKOLABS has officially opened on the 10/10/10 in Dakar. The first Francophone African coworking space among 700 world pioneers to make and innovate differently together!

Today the initiative has spread to form a network of 6 Jokkolabs co-working spaces across 4 countries: Mali, Burkina Faso, France and Senegal.
All these spaces remain independent and responding to their members’ specific demands and tailored to the local contexts, while respecting the Jokkolab approach and adhering to the coworking manifesto."


